item.title: BOTTLE MATCH Badminton
item.author: Annie Mao,
item.description: After the ‘true’ CSM badminton team (in which only 2 out of 6 players were miners (GEOGRAPHERS)) won the trophy last year, this year, CSM surprisingly bothered to send their actual team (of course, a NO-MINER team) to London. However, neither waking up at 5.30am nor a 6-hour drive demolished their …
